0.4.0:

2003-12-05  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@usa.net>

	* PrefixSuffix now uses gnome-vfsmm to rename files, using
	the Gnome::Vfs::transfer_list() method.
	* There is now a progress bar.
	* It now shows dialogs if
	  - incorrect data has been entered.
	  - there are runtime failures.

